name: Revolution!
description:
UMBRELLACO. - VERY LIMITED SERIES
Deep red burnout tee with white florid - Womens & Men's S, M

Burnout tee, dyed deep red with white florid REVOLUTION print. 
Designed and hand dyed by the UMBRELLA Team. Front all-over print with white ink.

*material:
60% ringspun pima cotton, 40% polyester;
Fabric put through an extensive process for weathered and faded effects; 
Each striation in this dyed fabric captures true old vintage worn in feel; 
matching self fabric sleeves; garment dyed pigment; enzyme/silicone finish; side seamed; set in sleeves.

Here shown: Men's & Women's full sleeve burnout tees
Size: S, M - comfortable fits. very flexible fabric.
